 of an effective medium\ncontains local field contributions proportional to the resonant frequency and\nto the spectral line-width.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 21 Feb 2010 22:12:22 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Dec 2010 15:53:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 22 Feb 2011 20:18:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-23"}
